public static final class ModuleServiceGrpc.ModuleServiceBlockingStub extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<ModuleServiceGrpc.ModuleServiceBlockingStub>
A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service ModuleService. 
 ModuleService deals with modular resource registration
